The 2018 Digital Content Marketing Conference will take place on 28 November 2018 at The Venue in Melrose Arch. The event is aimed at marketing professionals and business owners who want to learn more about digital content marketing. Topics which will be covered include PR in the digital age, online media exposure, social media, online video, lead generation, and calculating ROI. The conference will feature top speakers, including Radio 702’s Aki Anastasiou, The Tech Lab’s Ryan Brunyee, communication strategist Sarah Britten, rain CMO Khaya Dlanga, Siatik’s Brett StClair, and 5TUDIO’s Uno De Waal. Tickets for the 2018 Digital Content Marketing Conference cost R1,995, but there is a big discount available when using the code below. Register here – 2018 Digital Content Marketing Conference website Discount Voucher Code – Marketing2018 Please note that only 25 tickets are available for the event at this discounted price, and these seats will be allocated on a first-come-first-served basis.